the convention
was in Rhode Island. And there
was just a

08:57.804 --> 08:59.639 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
small handful of delegates.

08:59.672 --> 09:05.245 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
More dramatically, I think,
there were some
reports that suggest that about
39 of the

09:05.278 --> 09:09.282 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
unpledged delegates that came
out of Pennsylvania
are going to back Donald Trump
on the first

09:09.315 --> 09:15.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
