43:08.119 --> 43:10.188 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the evidence in your eyes is
gray.

43:10.221 --> 43:14.759 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then imagine the doctor does
something
and they turn on color for
half-an-hour. And

43:14.792 --> 43:19.764 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
even if color goes away, for the
rest of your
life, you're going to know it's
real. And

43:19.797 --> 43:24.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that's kind of how it is for me.
They stimulated
me, and it was a temporary
thing.

43:25.002 --> 43:30.141 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The effects lasted for some
months, I would
say. Some of them faded away
quickly, some

43:30.174 --> 43:37.782 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
longer. And that built an
ability that's in
me today based on that real
experience. And

43:37.815 --> 43:42.220 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
it's something words and
teaching and talk
could never have achieved.

43:42.253 --> 43:47.358 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The premise of
the stimulation
wasn't that you don't have the
wiring, so

43:47.391 --> 43:51.062 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
to speak, to pick up on
emotional cues. It's
just that your wiring was almost
dormant.

43:51.095 --> 43:56.868 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN ELDER ROBISON: Well, you
know, the magical
thing is, the premise of the
experiment exploited

43:56.901 --> 44:01.072 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the hope that I did have the
wiring.

44:01.105 --> 44:07.011 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when they fired the energy
into my head,
it wasn't like this gradually
came on. It

44:07.044 --> 44:11.682 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
was like I went to bed and I
woke up and the
next morning, bang, it was
there. And I could,

44:11.716 --> 44:17.054 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
like, look in your eyes, and it
was like seeing
into your soul. And never in my
life did I

44:17.088 --> 44:21.592 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
have experience like that
before. So, it was
from nothing to everything.

44:21.626 --> 44:28.065 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: You know, one
of the things
that you point out is that you
were overwhelmed

44:28.099 --> 44:29.834 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
just by waves of emotion.

44:29.867 --> 44:32.803 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN ELDER ROBISON: Just you and
me talking
like this, I would look at you,
and I would

44:32.837 --> 44:41.045 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
