fear or something,
and I would almost be brought to
tears by

44:41.078 --> 44:42.947 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
an ordinary conversation.

44:42.980 --> 44:48.319 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that happened to me the
first day. I would
say, excuse me. I got to just
step away and

44:48.352 --> 44:50.187 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
