symptoms of
a concussion.

51:13.737 --> 51:18.175 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And according to Dr. Jeff
Bazarian of the
University of Rochester Medical
center, it's

51:18.208 --> 51:21.345 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
