to be able
to pick up on those, too.

51:21.378 --> 51:23.147 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. JEFF BAZARIAN, University of
Rochester
Medical Center: There are
football players

51:23.180 --> 51:26.583 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
