some mild
brain injury.

51:28.552 --> 51:32.823 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SASHA-ANN SIMONS: Over the
years, more companies
have introduced impact sensors
and more doctors

51:32.856 --> 51:34.825 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
