51:34.858 --> 51:36.927 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Bazarian says that wasn't always
the case.

51:36.961 --> 51:42.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DR. JEFF BAZARIAN: People would
say, these
problems that you're having are
not rooted

51:42.866 --> 51:46.704 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
