injury here.

51:54.011 --> 52:00.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SASHA-ANN SIMONS: There's an
adage in boxing
that the best defense is to not
get hit.

52:00.818 --> 52:06.623 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Arioli is a firm believer
